{
  "stem": "24409.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Until the people there returned, their names were taken because they tried to escape, and so they returned to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But some very smart people took-- did not try to go to this near border, but they took-- traveled to Italy, where there was no problem yet of refugees on the border.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they traveled to Germany, to France, and there was nothing yet in the passports against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no law yet that they couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they crossed into France with a very good neutral Austrian passport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Wolfgang [INAUDIBLE] was one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Chester, ?] a leading member of the Revisionist Party, Edmund [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Chester, ?] he lives here, now, in Washington.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He escaped the day after that to Italy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how opposed they were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they-- well, after this experience with the passport, they officially, no, unofficially surrendered to our action.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got money from them by the help of Stricker and by the help of the leader of the Assimilationists, Dr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Josef Ticho, T-I-C-H-O.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was the leader of the Assimilationists, and he was the Vice President of the Jewish [NON-ENGLISH], Jewish community, and by his help, too, we got money for the transport.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was our treasurer, and she took care of all this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My work as a person?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a lawyer?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't work with the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, getting the Jews out is what I mean.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we met and planned how we could organize the next transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was decided, it's not possible now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have to see how the-- we have to decide to get the permission from the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
